### ==========================================
### 1: AUTENTICAZIONE E GESTIONE UTENTI
### ==========================================

### 1.1 Login come ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "admin@unina.it",
  "rawPassword": "Admin01!"
}

> {% client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token) %}

### 1.2 Crea un nuovo utente (Richiede ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "MickeyMouse@unina.it",
  "username": "Mickey Mouse",
  "rawPassword": "Password?123",
  "repeatRawPassword": "Password?123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 1.3 Crea un nuovo lurker (Richiede ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "DonaldDuck@unina.it",
  "username": "Donald Duck",
  "rawPassword": "Impossibile!!!100",
  "repeatRawPassword": "Impossibile!!!100",
  "role": "LURKER"
}

### 1.4 Visualizza tutti gli utenti (Richiede ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 1.5 Visualizza utenti disponibili (Richiede ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/available
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 1.6 Login con Mickey Mouse
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "MickeyMouse@unina.it",
  "rawPassword": "Password?123"
}

> {% client.global.set("user_token", response.body.token) %}

### 1.7 Ottieni i dati dell'utente corrente
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### ==========================================
### 2: GESTIONE TAG
### ==========================================

### 2.1 Crea Tag "Frontend" (USER o ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frontend"
}

### 2.2 Crea Tag "Database" (USER o ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Database"
}

### 2.3 Visualizza tutti i Tags
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### ==========================================
### 3: CICLO DI VITA DELLE ISSUE
### ==========================================

### 3.1 Crea una Issue di tipo BUG
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Errore query SQL",
  "description": "La query di ricerca va in timeout",
  "priority": true,
  "type": "BUG",
  "tags": ["Database"]
}

### 3.2 Crea una Issue di tipo FEATURE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Aggiunta animazione",
  "description": "Animazione al click del bottone login",
  "priority": false,
  "type": "FEATURE",
  "tags": ["Frontend"]
}

### 3.3 Visualizza tutte le Issues (Senza filtri)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 3.4 Assegna la Issue 1 all'Utente Mickey Mouse" (Richiede ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "user": {
    "id": 2
  }
}

### 3.5 Aggiorna stato della Issue 3 (Passa a INPROGRESS)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/status
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "newStatus": "INPROGRESS"
}

### 3.6 Aggiorna stato della Issue 1 (Passa a RESOLVED)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/status
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "newStatus": "RESOLVED"
}

### 3.7 Visualizza la History della Issue 3
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/history
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3
}


### ==========================================
### 4: RICERCHE AVANZATE E FILTRI
### ==========================================

### 4 Login con Donald Duck
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "DonaldDuck@unina.it",
  "rawPassword": "Impossibile!!!100"
}

> {% client.global.set("lurker_token", response.body.token) %}


### 4.1 Cerca Issue per Tipo (BUG)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/search
Authorization: Bearer {{lurker_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "BUG"
}

### 4.2 Cerca Issue per Priorità (true) e Tag
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/search
Authorization: Bearer {{lurker_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": true,
  "tags": ["Database"]
}

### 4.3 Cerca Issue per Data di Creazione (Range)
# TODO: DA RIVEDERE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/search
Authorization: Bearer {{lurker_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startCreationDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endCreationDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59"
}

### 4.4 Cerca Issue per Data di Ultima modifica (Range)
# TODO: DA RIVEDERE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/search
Authorization: Bearer {{lurker_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startLastModifiedDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endLastModifiedDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59"
}


### ==========================================
### 5: TEST DI SICUREZZA E VALIDAZIONE
### ==========================================

### 5.1 Fallimento: Utente tenta di chiudere una Issue (Atteso: 403 Forbidden)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/close
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2
}

### 5.2 Fallimento: Utente tenta di assegnare una Issue (Atteso: 403 Forbidden)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": { "id": 4 },
  "user": { "id": 9 }
}

### 5.3 Fallimento: Creazione Issue con dati mancanti (Atteso: 400 Bad Request)
# Manca il titolo e il tipo per far scattare l'anno tazione Valid
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Descrizione senza titolo",
  "priority": true
}

### 5.4 Fallimento: Creazione Utente con password debole (Atteso: 400 Bad Request)
# Presuppone che l'annotazione ValidPassword richieda criteri specifici (es. maiuscola/speciale)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "errore@unina.it",
  "username": "User Errore",
  "rawPassword": "123",
  "repeatRawPassword": "123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 5.5 Fallimento: Creazione di Issue da parte di lurker (Atteso: 403 Access Denied)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{lurker_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Issue malvagia",
  "description": "Questa non la risolverete mai",
  "priority": true,
  "type": "BUG"
}